WEBVTT

32:17.960 --> 32:19.150 line:80%
Now, people in town

32:19.150 --> 32:21.050 line:80%
probably all think I'm a she-devil.

32:19.460 --> 32:20.530 line:80%
♪ I pray that our love ♪

32:20.560 --> 32:23.250 line:80%
♪ Will never end ♪

32:22.570 --> 32:24.730 line:80%
A gambling house even sent me an offer,

32:23.920 --> 32:24.800 line:80%
♪ It's worth my foolishly waiting ♪

32:24.820 --> 32:27.200 line:80%
♪ For a lifetime ♪

32:25.310 --> 32:27.590 line:80%
saying if I don't butcher pigs
in the future,
